T1  - Is the minimum chi-square estimator the winner in logit regression?
AU  - Hughes, Gordon A
AU  - Savin, N.E
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 61
IS  - 2
SP  - 345
EP  - 366
PY  - 1994
