KW  - Restricted least squares estimator
KW  - Unidentified model
AB  - When some of explanatory variables are correlated with regression errors, the standard econometric theory advocates the use of instrumental variables estimators. This paper considers a special case where applied researchers do not have a sufficient number of instruments but instead they do have prior information on parameters in the form of parameter restrictions. The paper proposes a simple method of estimation and hypothesis testing in the above context. The results are extended to restricted GMM estimation in nonlinear context.
